{"tid":565872,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗睇利記 魔迷唔高興","createTime":"2018-02-19T11:38:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T13:13:08.000Z","uid":122,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"46102a838902429373fc958d1713d87f8ebeb248","tid":565872,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T11:38:44.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=vmKD4W8mTms%2Fq90gnFo94k%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=18dde629\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】一日紅魔，一世紅魔？大紅人基斯坦奴朗拿度近日在社交網站的短片，引起前東家曼聯粉絲不滿，原因何在？<br />\n<br />\n周日西甲又入波的33歲超級巨星基斯坦奴朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo），不經不覺由曼聯改投皇家馬德里已經9年，日前與女友洛迪古絲一邊擲波波，一邊看電視，並上載短片與網民分享。<br />\n<br />\n只是背景惹禍，C朗和女友被發現正在觀看歐聯利物浦大勝波圖的賽事，導致被部份魔迷留言「投訴」，認為他不該欣賞曼聯死敵利物浦的比賽。其實，上載短片的是洛迪古絲，而非C朗，而且大紅人好勝心強，一直專心擲波波，未必專注看球賽。魔迷是否太緊張？<br />\n<br />\n最近，C朗狀態已有起色，歐聯16強首回合對巴黎聖日耳門時梅開二度領軍輕取3:1，而他剛在西甲對貝迪斯亦有入球。"},{"pid":"4da072187fc74e533e68c037a78f5245e4e92d8a","tid":565872,"uid":50385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T12:03:07.000Z","msg":"支持波圖唔得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea15233990c09b8160eb2406d9e09afbce665912","tid":565872,"uid":81037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4da072187fc74e533e68c037a78f5245e4e92d8a","tid":565872,"uid":50385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T12:03:07.000Z","msg":"支持波圖唔得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T12:18:41.000Z","msg":"士砵亭死敵都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7488cbd6b8ae1fffd34248898bb6e54d8b1b74ed","tid":565872,"uid":158933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T12:53:15.000Z","msg":"又一例子證明獌狗玻璃心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj